""" Pyenv (documentation) """
# https://github.com/pyenv/pyenv?tab=readme-ov-file#a-getting-pyenv
# https://blog.stephane-robert.info/docs/developper/programmation/python/pyenv/
# https://blog.teclado.com/how-to-use-pyenv-manage-python-versions/

To check python versions and virtualenv installed:
	pyenv versions
	
Install a Python version:
	pyenv install [3.11.0]
	
Create a virtualenv:
	pyenv virtualenv [3.11.0] [name-of-my-venv]

Use a virtualenv:
	pyenv activate [name-of-my-venv]
	pyenv deactivate
	

